CRITICAL FIXES:
1. MEMORY LEAK PREVENTION
   • PlayerRemoving event cleans ActiveDrags & LastDrag tables
   • CharacterAdded disconnects old connections before creating new ones
   • All coroutines wrapped in pcall with error logging

2. RACE CONDITION HANDLING
   • Check victim.Parent before each operation in drag coroutine
   • Check char.Parent during heartbeat to prevent errors on respawn
   • Validate torso exists before suppressing signals

3. PERFORMANCE OPTIMIZATIONS
   • Spatial culling: skip players beyond Size * 1.5
   • Frame staggering: check 1/3 of players per frame (3-frame rotation)
   • Cached player data: avoid repeated FindFirstChild calls
   • Early exit: stop checking if already at max concurrent drags

4. ENHANCED ERROR HANDLING
   • All coroutine bodies wrapped in pcall
   • Error messages logged with warn() for debugging
   • Signal suppression/restoration wrapped in pcall
   • Character destruction handled gracefully

5. TEAM AWARENESS (CONFIGURABLE)
   • CFG.Filters.IgnoreTeam prevents dragging teammates
   • CFG.Filters.IgnoreFriends prevents dragging friends (requires Roblox API)
   • CFG.Filters.Whitelist/Blacklist for specific players

